 Festivals |publisher=Chinese Intercontinental Press <!--|ISBN=750850836X --> |isbn=978-7-5085-0836-8}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=kippas1919>{{cite book | first1=John Robert | last1=Kippax | date=1919 | title=The Call of the Stars: A Popular Introduction to a Knowledge of the Starry Skies with their Romance and Legend | url=https://archive.org/details/callstarsapopul01kippgoog | publisher=G. P. Putnam's Sons }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=boyce1996>{{cite book | first=Mary | last=Boyce | date=1996 | title=A History of Zoroastrianism, volume one: The Early Period | publisher=E. J. Brill | location=New York | isbn=978-90-04-08847-4 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=vartak20_75>{{cite book | last=Vartak | first=P. V | title=The Seminar on the Mahabharatha War | volume=20 | pages=75\u201383 | date=May 1992}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=tyson1993>{{cite book | first1=Donald | display-authors=1 | last1=Tyson | last2=Freake | first2=James | date=1993 | title=Three Books of Occult Philosophy | publisher=Llewellyn Worldwide | isbn=978-0-87542-832-1 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=argippa1533>{{cite book | first=Heinrich Cornelius | last=Agrippa | date=1533 | title=De Occulta Philosophia | isbn=978-90-04-09421-5 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=burnham1978>{{cite book | first=Robert J. R. | last=Burnham | date=1978 | title=Burnham's Celestial Handbook: An Observer's Guide to the Universe Beyond the Solar System | volume=2 | publisher=Courier Dover Publications | isbn=978-0-486-23568-4 | url-access=registration | url=https://archive.org/details/burnhamscelestia02robe }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=frommert>{{cite web | last=Frommert | first=Hartmut | url=http://yuridrive.yurisnight.net/~spider/spider/Misc/alphaLyr.html | title=Vega, Alpha Lyrae | publisher=SEDS | accessdate=2007-11-02 | url-status=dead | archiveurl=https://archive.today/20071024205329/http://yuridrive.yurisnight.net/~spider/spider/Misc/alphaLyr.html | archivedate=2007-10-24 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=esa20050520>{{cite web | author=Staff | date=2005-05-20 | url=http://www.esa.int/